thread.title: BRIEF-Kuwait Business Town Real Estate FY Proft Flat at 3.2 Mln Dinars

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Kuwait Business Town Real Estate FY Proft Flat at 3.2 Mln Dinars
text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - KUWAIT BUSINESS TOWN REAL ESTATE CO KSCP :
* FY NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO SHAREHOLDERS 3.2 ‍​MILLION DINARS VERSUS 3.2 ‍​MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* FY TOTAL OPERATING REVENUE 5.4 ‍​MILLION DINARS VERSUS 5.6 ‍​MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* BOARD PROPOSES CASH DIVIDEND OF 3 FILS PER SHARE FOR 2017
* BOARD PROPOSES STOCK DIVIDEND OF 5 SHARES PER EVERY 100 SHARES FOR 2017 Source: ( bit.ly/2EGNS12 )] Further company coverage:
